          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Bah. [Leave]" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Quinn_01_1c_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Good. I'm good. Taking it ahead easy: one day at a time. Your rat-juice took me to some places I needed to go."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You're cured?" linkto "Quinn_01_1c_3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I found the beast that took your wife. It's dead." linkto "Quinn_03b_1"  notes "This option only appears if the PC has killed the deathclaw AND Quinn has been cured."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I had a few questions for you." linkto "Quinn_09"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Never mind." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Old man brain-fixed?" linkto "Quinn_01_1c_3"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I killed bad nightmare-man! Look at me!" linkto "Quinn_03b_1"  notes "This option only appears if the PC has killed the deathclaw AND Quinn has been cured."
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL Gender=MALE playertext "<PC> got a thing he want ask old man." linkto "Quinn_09"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL Gender=FEMALE playertext "<PC> got a thing she want ask old man." linkto "Quinn_09"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Bah. [Leave]" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Quinn_01_1c_3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "In a kinda way, I don't think I ever was really ill. It's just... funny the way the mind plays tricks when you ignore the things you need to take care of the most."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[More]" linkto "Quinn_01_1c_4"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[More]" linkto "Quinn_01_1c_4"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Quinn_01_1c_4"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Anyway, thanks, if I didn't say so before. What can I do for you?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I found the beast that took your wife. It's dead." linkto "Quinn_03b_1"  notes "This option only appears if the PC has killed the deathclaw AND Quinn has been cured."
