Node "Quinn_01_1F_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "About time, Polly. Why, a man could die of thirstiness in the time it takes you to... What's this then? What've you done?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What are you talking about? Who's Polly?" linkto "Quinn_01_1F_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Who are you?" linkto "Quinn_01_2"  notes "if PC has never heard of quinn"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "My name's <PC>. I've come to ask you some questions." linkto "Quinn_09"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Never mind." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Quinn_01_1F_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Ah, my Polly. Those eyes, those eyes. Eyes and worms and flies. But you're not her! So what is it?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I want to know what happened to your wife." linkto "Quinn_02_3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about this town of yours." linkto "Quinn_07_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Nothing, forget it." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Quinn_01_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = true
{
NPCText "Why, I can't believe you'd need to ask. I'm the Captain of this fine boat. Captain Quinn! Best remember the name, boy."
 NPCFemaleText "Why, I can't believe you'd need to ask. I'm the Captain of this fine boat. Captain Quinn! Best remember the name, girl."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[More]" linkto "Quinn_01_3"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Quinn_01_3"
notes ""
is_wtg = true
{
NPCText "So that's me. What about you? What're you here for?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I want to know what happened to your wife." linkto "Quinn_02_3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about this town of yours." linkto "Quinn_07_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Don't mind me. I was just leaving." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Quinn_02_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "'Til death do us apart, for richer or poorer. My lovely lady wife, her guts for garters."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Polly's your wife?" linkto "Quinn_02_2a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What was that about guts?" linkto "Quinn_02_2b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you a question about something else?" linkto "Quinn_09"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I was just leaving." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Guts?" linkto "Quinn_02_2b"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "<PC> want ask a question about another thing." linkto "Quinn_09"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[Leave]" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Quinn_02_2a"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Aye, my pretty parrot. That she be, all inside out and made of muss."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What was that about guts?" linkto "Quinn_02_2b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL Gender=MALE playertext "You thought I'd done something to Polly when we first met. Has she been missing?" linkto "Quinn_02_3"  notes "This is not the first time the PC has spoken to Quinn; the PC is male."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL Gender=FEMALE playertext "You thought I was Polly when we first spoke. Has she been missing?" linkto "Quinn_02_3"  notes "This is not the first time the PC has spoken to Quinn; the PC is female."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL Gender=MALE playertext "You said earlier you thought I'd done something to Polly. Has she been missing?" linkto "Quinn_02_3"  notes "This is the first time the PC has spoken to Quinn; the PC is male."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL Gender=FEMALE playertext "You said earlier you thought I was Polly. Has she been missing?" linkto "Quinn_02_3"  notes "This is the first time the PC has spoken to Quinn; the PC is female."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you a question about something else?" linkto "Quinn_09"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I was just leaving." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Guts?" linkto "Quinn_02_2b"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Where you think Polly lady-parrot is?" linkto "Quinn_02_3"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "<PC> want ask a question about another thing." linkto "Quinn_09"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[Leave]" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Quinn_02_2b"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Gizzards and innards and dangly things. We're all made of 'em, boy. Some of us see more of them than most."
 NPCFemaleText "Gizzards and innards and dangly things. We're all made of 'em, girl. Some of us see more of them than most."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Polly's your wife?" linkto "Quinn_02_2a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL Gender=MALE playertext "You thought I'd done something to Polly when we first met. Has she been missing?" linkto "Quinn_02_3"  notes "This is not the first time the PC has spoken to Quinn; the PC is male."
