          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL Gender=MALE playertext "You said earlier you thought I'd done something to Polly. Has she been missing?" linkto "Quinn_02_3"  notes "This is the first time the PC has spoken to Quinn; the PC is male."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL Gender=FEMALE playertext "You said earlier you thought I was Polly. Has she been missing?" linkto "Quinn_02_3"  notes "This is the first time the PC has spoken to Quinn; the PC is female."
