Node "Quinn_02_3"
notes "The Quinn_06_* path is where the PC can find out from Quinn about his wife."
is_wtg = true
{
NPCText "My Polly. The brute took her bones and the sea took her blood and all I'm left with are these worms in my throat."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Some people say you killed her." linkto "Quinn_02_4a"  notes "If the PC has heard rumours about the death in CotC."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What brute? Who are you talking about?" linkto "Quinn_02_4b_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me what happened." linkto "Quinn_02_4b_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you about something else?" linkto "Quinn_09"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks for clearing that up. Bye." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "<PC> hear you kill Polly!" linkto "Quinn_02_4a"  notes "If the PC has heard rumours about the death in CotC."
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What this brute?" linkto "Quinn_02_4b_2"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell <PC> more." linkto "Quinn_02_4b_1"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Now <PC> got an ask about another thing." linkto "Quinn_09"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[Leave]" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Quinn_02_4a"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "They say, they say! Well I say they can have her! They can clean their teeth on her guts for what I care! I don't want her anymore, I don't want her blood tasting in my mouth, I don't want these flies' eggs in my belly. I want her out!"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me what happened to her." linkto "Quinn_02_4b_1"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell <PC> more." linkto "Quinn_02_4b_1"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Quinn_02_4b_1"
notes ""
is_wtg = true
{
NPCText "Nothing left to tell. Her blood grew worms. They swam away. Now there's only me and him. The brute."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "The brute? Who are you talking about?" linkto "Quinn_02_4b_2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I've heard it said you killed her." linkto "Quinn_02_4a"  notes "If the PC has heard rumours about the death in CotC."
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What this brute? Tell more." linkto "Quinn_02_4b_2"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "<PC> hear you kill Polly." linkto "Quinn_02_4a"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Quinn_02_4b_2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "The beast! Oh, that brute, I saw him I did! Dipped in blood up to his neck, all claws and teeth and eyes deep as the night sky, colder, emptier still. Came out of the night mist and snapped her all to bits."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[More]" linkto "Quinn_02_4b_3"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[More]" linkto "Quinn_02_4b_3"  notes ""
              }
}
