{
NPCText "Then... I'm locked in this box, boiling in my own skull meat, while you - stranger! - are out killing the brute? Killing the beast! What have you done to me?"
      options {
          int=4 linkflags skill_check Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I avenged your wife. What's the problem here?" linkto "Skill_03a_2b_3a"  notes ""
          int=4 linkflags skill_check Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You don't sound as grateful as I thought you'd be." linkto "Skill_03a_2b_3a"  notes ""
          int=4 linkflags skill_check Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Don't be too hard on yourself. There's no way you could've killed it, old as you are." linkto "Skill_03a_2b_3b"  notes ""
          int=4 linkflags skill_check Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I assumed there'd be some kind of reward for this." linkto "Skill_03a_2b_3c"  notes ""
          int=-3 linkflags skill_check Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Old man looks mad. Did I do it wrong?" linkto "Skill_03a_2b_3a"  notes ""
          int=-3 linkflags skill_check Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Yes! Can I have some money?" linkto "Skill_03a_2b_3c"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Quinn_03a_2b_4a"
notes ""
is_wtg = true
{
NPCText "She wasn't yours! It was all mine, and now she's dead, and who are you? Nobody, that's who! Tomorrow you'll be gone with everyone else, and she'll be dead."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Listen, crazy man. I killed the beast that killed your wife. Wasn't that what you wanted?" linkto "Quinn_03a_2b_5a_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I guess a reward is out of the question?" linkto "Quinn_03a_2b_4c"  notes ""
