Node "Quinn_08_01"
notes "The Quinn_08_* path is where the PC learns about CotC's origins, and the whaler ship's role in them."
is_wtg = true
{
NPCText "We call the day the City was founded Landfall Day. Take a moment and I'll tell yer how it came to be."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm listening." linkto "Quinn_08_02"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Actually, can I ask you about something else, instead?" linkto "Quinn_09"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe another time. Goodbye for now." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "<PC> heard this story before! Another!" linkto "Quinn_08_11D" conditions { LOCAL_VARIABLE LVAR_Quinn_Story_Before > 0 link_next NONE } notes "If Quinn has spoken the Quinn_08_02 node before."
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Story? Yay!" linkto "Quinn_08_02"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "<PC> hear enough. Got another ask for old man." linkto "Quinn_09"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Nah. [Leave]" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Quinn_08_02"
notes "Set LVAR_Quinn_Story_Before to 1."
is_wtg = true
{
NPCText "Great days, terrible days they were back then, and all men alive were at war. This ship, this very ship you're standing in, was lost in the waters. Lost far beyond the farthest point, where waves are ten times higher than a man and there's not a speck of sand wherever you look."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Go on." linkto "Quinn_08_03"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I get the picture. It's not an interesting picture. Let's change the subject." linkto "Quinn_09"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks for the story. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[Listen]" linkto "Quinn_08_03"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "<PC> hear enough. Got another ask for old man." linkto "Quinn_09"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Boring. [Leave]" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Quinn_08_03"
notes ""
is_wtg = true
{
NPCText "Well, then the bombs got to fallin' - folks call it the Great War. This here ship and many others like her were out to sea when their harbor was hit by the bombs - boom! - nuked to ashes, she were."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[More]" linkto "Quinn_08_04"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[More]" linkto "Quinn_08_04"  notes ""
              }
}
